                    <physDesc>
                        <objectDesc form="codex">
                            <supportDesc material="perg">
                                <support>
                                    <p>Parchment.</p>
                                </support>
                                <extent>2 conjoint fragment-leaves. <dimensions type="leaf"
                                        scope="all">
                                        <height unit="mm">167</height>
                                        <width unit="mm">157</width>
                                    </dimensions>
                                </extent>
                                <condition>
                                    <p>The two leaves are trimmed causing a loss of text; the last 4
                                        lines of both of the leaves are now missing, furthermore a
                                        good part of the outer columns of f. 2 is cut away. The
                                        outer leaves i.e. ff. 1r and especially 2v are so worn that
                                        reading at some parts is made difficult or impossible; f.
                                        2vb is more or less illegible. The ink in two of the
                                        initials, S and Þ, on f. 2r have contained a copper
                                        connection that has corroded the vellum, the lower bow of
                                        the S missing, whereas nothing but the hole and some few
                                        ornamentations is left of the Þ.</p>
                                </condition>
                            </supportDesc>
                            <layoutDesc>
                                <layout columns="2" writtenLines="31 32">
                                    <p>Written in double columns with 32 and 31 extant lines to the
                                        column on ff. 1 and 2, respectively.</p>
                                </layout>
                            </layoutDesc>
